short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Meet Dr. Kevin Molldrem | Molldrem Family Dentistry

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Since opening Molldrem Family Dentistry in Eden Prairie, Minnesota in June 2004, Dr. Kevin Molldrem has been committed to providing the same quality of dental care he would want for his own family. With extensive training and experience, Dr. Molldrem and his team address each family's unique dental needs with expertise and compassion.

Dedicated to ongoing education, Dr. Molldrem embraces the latest technologies and less invasive treatments to ensure patients receive top-notch care. Since 1999, he has been making a difference in patients' lives, helping them maintain healthy, bright smiles.

Outside the office, Dr. Molldrem enjoys spending time with his three daughters—Georgia, Francesca, and Addison—and their two cats. Together, they love scuba diving, snowboarding, and wakesurfing.

Experience honest, trustworthy dental care with Dr. Kevin Molldrem, where your family's smile is the priority.
